    <item>
      <title>债券交易商期待拍卖创纪录，标志着 5% 收益率已达峰值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/bond-traders-look-to-record-auction-for-sign-5-yield-is-peak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国国债有望迎来今年最糟糕的一个月，大量拍卖即将到来，这是对收益率在达到 2024 年最高水平后是否已见顶的重大考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/bond-traders-look-to-record-auction-for-sign-5-yield-is-peak</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利对中国钢铁征收关税以支持当地工业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/chile-slaps-tariffs-on-chinese-steel-to-bolster-local-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利对该国采矿业使用的中国钢铁产品征收临时反倾销关税，以支持摇摇欲坠的当地钢厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/chile-slaps-tariffs-on-chinese-steel-to-bolster-local-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 18:11:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肖尔茨对德国经济持乐观态度，理由是通胀和就业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/scholz-optimistic-on-german-economy-citing-inflation-and-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨对德国的经济前景持乐观态度，他表示，由于能源成本下降，就业率创历史新高，通胀放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/scholz-optimistic-on-german-economy-citing-inflation-and-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 17:56:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戴蒙会见寻求私人资金的开发银行领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/dimon-meets-with-development-bank-leaders-seeking-private-money</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司首席执行官杰米·戴蒙 (Jamie Dimon) 会见了世界银行集团和其他几家多边开发贷款机构的高管，他们寻求将更多私人资金引入新兴市场的举措中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/dimon-meets-with-development-bank-leaders-seeking-private-money</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 17:55:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着伯南克提出替代方案，美联储的预测方法看起来越来越过时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/fed-s-forecasting-method-looks-increasingly-outdated-as-bernanke-pitches-new-way</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储陷入了一种看起来越来越有限的预测和公共沟通模式，尤其是在经济不断带来惊喜的情况下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/fed-s-forecasting-method-looks-increasingly-outdated-as-bernanke-pitches-new-way</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 12:42:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚将削减预算中的主要全球经济增长预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/australia-to-cut-key-global-economy-growth-forecasts-in-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财长吉姆·查尔默斯表示，澳大利亚将在下个月发布预算时下调包括主要贸易伙伴中国在内的大多数主要经济体的增长前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/australia-to-cut-key-global-economy-growth-forecasts-in-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织面临反对新兴市场债务重做蓝图的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/pressure-mounts-at-imf-against-blueprint-for-em-debt-reworks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界金融领导人正在推动彻底改革主权债务重组体系，该体系使贫穷国家被排除在资本市场之外，因为中国作为关键参与者的出现颠覆了传统谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/pressure-mounts-at-imf-against-blueprint-for-em-debt-reworks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基辅希望重新夺回主动权，泽伦斯基欢呼美国的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/war-in-ukraine-us-military-assistance-could-come-soon-after-house-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰当局对美国众议院批准超过 600 亿美元的援助感到欢欣鼓舞，不过焦点已转移到援助能以多快的速度到达前线，以及该计划将如何改变基辅在对抗俄罗斯入侵的斗争中的命运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/war-in-ukraine-us-military-assistance-could-come-soon-after-house-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 11:05:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储首选通胀指标将支持降息耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/us-rate-cuts-latest-fed-s-preferred-inflation-gauge-is-set-to-back-patience</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储官员即将得到进一步确认，证明对抗通胀的进展已陷入停滞，这支持了基调的转变，将利率维持在比先前预期更长的时间内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/us-rate-cuts-latest-fed-s-preferred-inflation-gauge-is-set-to-back-patience</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
